                <layoutDesc>
                  <layout columns="1" rulingMedium="hardpoint" subtype="fullWidth" topLine="below" type="fragment" writtenLines="30">ff. <locus from="8v/1r" to="2v/7r">1r-2v</locus>, <locus from="5v/4r" to="5v/4r">4r-5v</locus>, <locus from="2v/7r" to="8v/1r">7r-8v</locus> A single column of 30 lines,
