                  <layout columns="1" rulingMedium="hardpoint" topLine="below" type="fragment" writtenLines="26">ff. <locus from="6v/3r" to="3v/6r">3r-3v</locus>, <locus from="3v/6r" to="6v/3r">6r-6v</locus> A single column of 26 surviving lines,
