              <handDesc>
                <handNote scope="major" xml:id="hand-1"> The lower text of ff. <locus from="8v/1r" to="2v/7r">1r-2v</locus>, <locus from="5v/4r" to="5v/4r">4r-5v</locus>, <locus from="2v/7r" to="8v/1r">7r-8v</locus> was copied by Hand A, in an upright <term type="script">mixed minuscule Perlschrift</term> in brown ink, with minimal
